description:
Give us back our freedom!!
🇺🇸
Let’s do our research & look into the ACTUAL facts of what’s going on.. we are being lied to!!
🦅
It’s time to reopen California.
FREEDOM IS ESSENTIAL!!!
Repost: @corieclark 
FREEDOM KEEPER

I may not have to go to “war” but I will fight the war within this nation as long as there is breath in my lungs. 
I will fight for TRUTH. 
I will fight for medical freedom.
I will fight for your right to wear a mask if that’s what you want.
I will show my children (not just tell them) to speak truth even when others are too afraid to.
I will fight for our constitution. Every last letter of it. 
I will not go down without a fight. 
Freedom is not free. 🇺🇸
